data_table.description: Lab Assay: Red Blood Cell Fatty Acid (blood), Generation 3 and Omni 2 Exam 2. Fatty acid composition was determined with gas chromatography. Results are calculated as the percentage of total fatty acids, compared to a standard mixture of fatty acids characteristic of RBCs.
